entry.def: If you try to reproduce something, you try to copy it.

example.ex: I shall not try to reproduce the policemen's English...
example.tran: 我不会试图去模仿那个警察讲的英语。

example.ex: The effect has proved hard to reproduce.
example.tran: 事实证明，这种效果很难再现。

entry.def: If you reproduce a picture, speech, or a piece of writing, you make a photograph or printed copy of it.

example.ex: We are grateful to you for permission to reproduce this article.
example.tran: 非常感谢您允许我们复印这篇文章。

entry.def: If you reproduce an action or an achievement, you repeat it.

example.ex: If we can reproduce the form we have shown in the last couple of months we will be successful.
example.tran: 如果我们能再采用前两个月的形式，我们就会成功。

entry.def: When people, animals, or plants reproduce, they produce young.

example.ex: ...a society where women are defined by their ability to reproduce...
example.tran: 用生育能力衡量女性价值的社会

example.ex: We are reproducing ourselves at such a rate that our numbers threaten the ecology of the planet.
example.tran: 我们的繁衍速度太快，以至于人口数量对地球的生态系统造成了威胁。
